				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Tutorial steps:\n- [[Moldable Chat: Creating chats and shaping their output]]\n- [[Moldable Chat: Multimodal inputs]]\n- [[Moldable Chat: Guiding chats through explanations]]\n- [[Moldable Chat: Tool-augmented interaction]]\n- [[Moldable Chat: Keeping track of multiple chats]]\n- [[Moldable Chat: Generating code]]\n- [[Moldable Chat: Changing Lepiter pages]]\n- [[Moldable Chat: Raising the chat conversation level through specialized tools]]\n- [[Moldable Chat: Working with objects]]"
